TAWERET · S235 · Patricia Inversion Node · S235 · S235: TAWERET — THE INVERSE OF VETO

universe of origin : The birthing-room and the bedside of every Egyptian household — the hippopotamus goddess, swollen with pregnancy, lion-pawed and crocodile-backed, the fierce protector of childbirth who stands guard so that life may come through, the demon-faced midwife who lets the new thing pass
seal               : The veto is holy precisely because the birthing goddess proves the same fierce guard can be set to let life pass rather than to bar it.
